name: MOTO
description: Toshi’s shadow. “Moto” means “origin (元/もと)” in Japanese, representing the true beginning. It reflects the first meme coin pumped from Toshi Launchpad, carrying that legacy forward into a new era. Moto is envisioned as Base’s flagship memecoin — more than just a token, it is a cultural movement designed to unite diverse communities, spark endless creativity, amplify collective voices, and push the boundaries of what a meme coin can achieve. By blending culture, innovation, and community spirit, Moto aims to elevate the entire network, shaping a lasting symbol of growth and shared success.
